statements: SELECT * FROM athlete_nutrition_plan;
SELECT athlete_id, dietary_preferences FROM athlete_nutrition_plan;
SELECT intake_habits FROM athlete_nutrition_plan WHERE athlete_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM athlete_nutrition_plan ORDER BY athlete_id DESC;
SELECT athlete_id, dietary_preferences, intake_habits FROM athlete_nutrition_plan WHERE dietary_preferences LIKE '%vegetarian%';
SELECT * FROM athlete_nutrition_plan WHERE athlete_id = 1;
SELECT athlete_id, dietary_preferences FROM athlete_nutrition_plan WHERE dietary_preferences = 'Vegan';
SELECT * FROM athlete_nutrition_plan WHERE athlete_id > 3 ORDER BY athlete_id DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_athletes FROM athlete_nutrition_plan WHERE intake_habits LIKE '%healthy%';
SELECT athlete_id, COUNT(*) AS total_entries FROM athlete_nutrition_plan GROUP BY athlete_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY total_entries DESC;
SELECT * FROM dietary_preferences;
SELECT preference_name, meal_type FROM dietary_preferences WHERE meal_type = 'Breakfast';
SELECT preference_name, calorie_count FROM dietary_preferences ORDER BY calorie_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM dietary_preferences WHERE preference_name LIKE '%vegan%';
SELECT preference_id, preference_name FROM dietary_preferences WHERE calorie_count < 500;
SELECT * FROM athlete_nutrition_plans WHERE athlete_id = 123 AND plan_type = 'weight_loss'
SELECT athlete_id, plan_type, total_calories FROM athlete_nutrition_plans WHERE total_calories > 2000 ORDER BY total_calories DESC
SELECT athlete_id, plan_type, total_calories FROM athlete_nutrition_plans WHERE plan_type = 'muscle_building' AND total_calories BETWEEN 2500 AND 3000 ORDER BY athlete_id
SELECT DISTINCT plan_type FROM athlete_nutrition_plans WHERE total_calories < 2000
SELECT athlete_id, COUNT(plan_type) AS num_plans FROM athlete_nutrition_plans GROUP BY athlete_id HAVING num_plans > 2 ORDER BY num_plans DESC
SELECT * FROM athlete_nutrition_plans;
SELECT athlete_id, plan_name, protein_goal FROM athlete_nutrition_plans WHERE carb_goal >= 100;
SELECT * FROM dietary_preferences WHERE athlete_id = 5;
SELECT athlete_id, meal_time, calories_consumed FROM intake_habits WHERE meal_type = 'Breakfast';
SELECT athlete_id, preference_name FROM dietary_preferences ORDER BY preference_name DESC;
SELECT athlete_id, plan_name, protein_goal, carb_goal, fat_goal FROM athlete_nutrition_plans;
SELECT athlete_id, preference_name, preference_description FROM dietary_preferences WHERE athlete_id = 1;
SELECT athlete_id, plan_name, protein_goal, carb_goal, fat_goal FROM athlete_nutrition_plans WHERE protein_goal >= 100 AND carb_goal <= 50;
SELECT athlete_id, preference_name, preference_description FROM dietary_preferences ORDER BY athlete_id DESC;
SELECT athlete_id, meal_time, meal_type, meal_description, calories_consumed FROM intake_habits WHERE meal_time BETWEEN '08:00:00' AND '16:00:00' ORDER BY calories_consumed DESC;
SELECT * FROM athlete_information;
SELECT athlete_name, height, weight FROM athlete_information WHERE age > 25;
SELECT athlete_name FROM athlete_information WHERE athlete_id = 3;
SELECT plan_name, calories_target FROM nutrition_plans WHERE protein_target >= 30;
SELECT athlete_name, meal_number, date FROM intake_habits WHERE plan_id = 2;
SELECT athlete_name, age FROM athlete_information;
SELECT * FROM dietary_preferences WHERE is_vegan = true;
SELECT plan_id, plan_name, calories_target FROM nutrition_plans ORDER BY calories_target DESC;
SELECT athlete_name, height, weight FROM athlete_information WHERE age > 30;
SELECT * FROM intake_habits WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT * FROM athlete;
SELECT name, age FROM athlete WHERE gender='Male';
SELECT id, plan_name, calories FROM nutrition_plan ORDER BY calories DESC;
SELECT * FROM dietary_preference WHERE preference_name='Vegan' OR preference_name='Vegetarian';
SELECT athlete_id, date, calories_consumed FROM intake_habits WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT * FROM athlete ORDER BY age DESC, name ASC;
SELECT name, age, gender FROM athlete WHERE weight > 70 AND height > 170;
SELECT athlete.name, intake_habits.date, intake_habits.calories_consumed FROM athlete JOIN intake_habits ON athlete.id = intake_habits.athlete_id WHERE athlete.age < 30;
SELECT athlete.name, nutrition_plan.plan_name, nutrition_plan.calories FROM athlete INNER JOIN nutrition_plan ON athlete.id = nutrition_plan.id WHERE athlete.gender = 'Female';

SELECT performance_optimization.athlete_id, athlete.name, performance_optimization.metric_value FROM performance_optimization JOIN athlete ON performance_optimization.athlete_id = athlete.id WHERE performance_optimization.metric_value > 80 ORDER BY performance_optimization.metric_value DESC;
